<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Enhanced Whiteboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4A90E2;
            --secondary: #6c757d;
            --success: #28a745;
            --background: #000000;
            --text: #ffffff;
            --light: #333333;
            --shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .navbar {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px var(--shadow);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--shadow);
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .logo:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .logo i {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .main-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light) 0%, var(--background) 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px var(--shadow);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.2;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.2s backwards;
        }

        .buttons {
            margin: 2rem 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.4s backwards;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            margin: 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--light);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--light);
            color: var(--primary);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--light);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 4rem 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px var(--shadow);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px var(--shadow);
        }

        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover i {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .buttons {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 250px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="#" class="logo">
            <i class="fas fa-paint-brush"></i>
            Inkwave â€“ A creative and modern take on digital whiteboards.
        </a>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-content">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Collaborate and Create Together</h1>
            <p>Experience seamless collaboration with our enhanced digital whiteboard. Share ideas, sketch concepts, and bring your team's creativity to life.</p>
            <div class="buttons">
                <a href="/drawing" class="btn btn-primary">Start Drawing</a>
                <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features" id="features">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-pen-fancy"></i>
                <h3>Advanced Drawing Tools</h3>
                <p>Access a comprehensive set of drawing tools designed for both simplicity and precision.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                <h3>Real-time Collaboration</h3>
                <p>Work together seamlessly with your team members in real-time, from anywhere in the world.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-share-alt"></i>
                <h3>Easy Sharing</h3>
                <p>Share your work instantly with team members and stakeholders with just a few clicks.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
